<h1>Privacy Policy for SpaceLax</h1>
<p><strong>Effective Date:</strong> 31 December 2025</p>

<p>
SpaceLax is a casual, offline-first game designed for relaxation and entertainment.
Your privacy is important to us, and this app is built with minimal data usage in mind.
</p>

<h2>Information Collection</h2>
<p>
SpaceLax does not collect, store, or request any personal information from users.
No account creation, login, or personal identifiers are required to play the game.
</p>

<h2>Data Usage</h2>
<p>
All game data, such as progress and settings, is stored locally on the user’s device.
SpaceLax does not transmit any data to external servers.
</p>

<h2>Third-Party Services</h2>
<p>
SpaceLax does not use third-party analytics, advertising SDKs, or tracking services.
</p>

<h2>User Control</h2>
<p>
Users can remove all locally stored game data by clearing the app’s storage
or uninstalling the application from their device.
</p>

<h2>Children’s Privacy</h2>
<p>
SpaceLax is safe for all age groups and does not knowingly collect any data from children.
</p>

<h2>Contact</h2>
<p>
Developer: Ddevloper<br/>
App Name: SpaceLax
</p>

